    <h1>Professional LG Dryer Repair Services in Los Angeles</h1>
    <p>Your LG dryer starts making that grinding noise during the spin cycle, and suddenly your Saturday laundry plans are ruined. We see this scenario play out dozens of times each week across Los Angeles — usually it's a worn drum roller or bad idler pulley, and our technicians can have it running quietly again the same day.</p>
